RobitDroid
==========

RobitDroid is a game where the computer guesses a number, by answering
questions with 'Yes' and 'No'.

It is a port of Robit (https://github.com/kennym/robit) to the Android
platform.

How does it work?
-----------------

You can read the source code, to understand the algorithm. It's dead
simple actually, and some people understand the algorithm after a few
games.

Bugs and feature requests
-------------------------

Please, report any issues here: https://github.com/kennym/RobitDroid/issues